34:25.591 --> 34:27.891
Margaret: I thought maybe
lemon chicken for dinner?

34:27.927 --> 34:30.060
Jo: With those scalloped
potatoes you make?

34:30.112 --> 34:32.146
Those are so good.
You have to teach me.

34:32.197 --> 34:35.199
Margaret: Potatoes.
Heavy cream.

34:35.234 --> 34:40.003
Jo: So, how did it go
with those new exercises?

34:41.040 --> 34:43.489
Margaret:
Well, it's too soon to say.

34:43.542 --> 34:45.125
