on my own.

36:37.690 --> 36:39.740
You were not part of that, Jo.

36:39.775 --> 36:42.359
We didn't have any problems
in bed or anywhere else

36:42.411 --> 36:43.860
until you came along.

36:43.912 --> 36:46.296
Graham:
Margaret, I won't have it.

36:46.332 --> 36:48.532
Margaret: Why did you
bring her into this?

36:48.534 --> 36:50.450
Graham: I didn't do anything.
