39:17.266 --> 39:19.816
of people at Wash U
who had you fired.

39:19.852 --> 39:21.818
William:
There's a reason for that.

39:21.854 --> 39:24.287
It <i> is</i> the petition list.

39:32.865 --> 39:35.415
Libby: That was Dennis
Daughtry's mother on the phone.

39:35.451 --> 39:38.034
